{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dafa299fac","title":"给赛福鼎和帕哈太克里乡农民的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c27eef2658","index":0,"year":1952,"month":8,"day":30,"articleId":"dafa299fac"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4fb516c89b","type":"title","text":"给赛福鼎和帕哈太克里乡农民的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"07f73e7fad","type":"paragraph","text":"赛福鼎同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"c01d96cd65","type":"paragraph","text":"根据你的意见，对疏附县帕哈太克里乡的农民同志们的来信，写了一封回信，烦为转交为荷！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"73ab42b8f7","type":"paragraph","text":"致以同志的敬礼！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"fba38676c8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"38fd4f283d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年八月开日喀什区蔬附县帕哈太克里乡全体农民同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"09c803164f","type":"paragraph","text":"感谢你们今年三月在庆祝土地改革胜利时写给我的信。你们已经从地主阶级封建土地所有制的束缚中获得解放，希望你们在爱国","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"a254861e26","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]赛福鼎，即赛福鼎·艾则孜，当时任中央人民政府委员、新疆省人民政府副主席。丰产的口号之下，更加团结，努力生产，改善自己的物质生活；并在这个基础之上，一步一步地提高自己的文化水平。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"09bb59f2d0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"dafa299fac"},{"id":"4463f37c0d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年八月三十日","i